After finding it, he oversees the content and checks if it’s still up to date. 
He finds a few flaws in one document, so he wants to improve this file. 
He opens the file by clicking on the document name, than he clicks on the „Edit this file“ - button (pencil icon on the right side), 
he changes the specific points by deleting them and writing it new, he scrolls to the end of the site, 
selects the bullet „Commit directly to the main branch“ and clicks on the „Commit changes“ - button. 
Now the website shows the changed document, the methodology of the old training is updated. 
